name: Lilith
description:
Her presence was ethereal yet bestial.
She was unclothed, not even her modesty was covered by any fur.
Her eyes glowed white like the moon illuminating her figure.
It’s not her that piqued my interest but a deer skull on her neck.
Steamed heaved through the cracks of its skull.
She is Lilith, The Dark Mother.

Inspired and based on a scene from a novel, The Year of the Witching by Alexis Henderson.
